gobblin.source.workunit

Class WorkUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.configuration.State
      • gobblin.source.workunit.WorkUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WritableShim
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImmutableWorkUnit, MultiWorkUnit

    public class WorkUnit
extends State
    A logic concept that defines a unit of work or task for extracting a portion of the data to be pulled in a job run.

    An instance of this class should contain all the properties an Extractor needs to extract the schema and data records.
